The Keiser Report  No. 163			
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 12 July 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy report on declaring war on rating agencies and buying refrigerators to save the economy. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to Professor Emeritus, Guy McPherson, who has exited empire to build a post-carbon community.

 that counters the monotone of mainstream corporate media.
